snippet.title: Ryan Burke Pictures
snippet.description:
Hi, My name is Ryan Francis Burke. I am 17 years old and I have autism. My favourite movie is Kung Fu Panda, Atlantis, Rio, Happy Feet, Legend of the Guardians, Justin and the Knights of Valour, Alpha and Omega, Khumba, The Iron Giant, Shrek, Madagascar, Roadside Romeo and others. My favourite TV show is Disney’s Recess. I also like all live-action movies. My favourite composer is Hans Zimmer. 

Please welcome my favourite characters Po the Panda, Milo Thatch, Hogarth, Blu, Nico, Pedro, Justin, TJ and the gang, Mumble, Soren, Felicie and others. I'm a huge fan of films. On my channel I will be uploading songs, different movie clips, please like and subscribe to my videos and I hope you enjoy.
